Agent(pipeline/stage level)
============================
1.agent any
2.agent none
3.agent { 
     label 'my-defined-label' 
  }
4.agent { 
     node { 
       label 'labelName' 
     }
  }

it is same as label but it allows for additional option such as customWorkspace

agent { 
     node { 
       label 'labelName' 
       customWorkspace '/some/other/path'
     }
  }

5.for docker 
==============
agent { 
  docker 'maven:3-alpine' 
}
or
agent { 
   docker {
      label 'my-defined-label' 
   }
}
6. stage level
===================
pipeline {
    agent none 
    stages {
        stage('Example Build') {
            agent { docker 'maven:3-alpine' } 
            steps {
                echo 'Hello, Maven'
                sh 'mvn --version'
            }
        }
        stage('Example Test') {
            agent { docker 'openjdk:8-jre' } 
            steps {
                echo 'Hello, JDK'
                sh 'java -version'
            }
        }
    }
}

